title: Aikido - Shoji Nishio Sensei - complete DVD series (Vol. 1-6)
description:
Contains the following Volumes of this great Aikido master:

Vol. 1: Gyakuhanmi Katatedori 
Vol. 2: Aihanmi Katatedori
Vol. 3: Shomenuchi 1
Vol. 4: Shomenuchi 2
Vol. 5: Yokomenuchi 
Vol. 6: Ryotedori-Sodedori

Enjoy!

PS: If you have other instructional Aikido videos, please make them available to the community. 
And don't forget: Sharing is caring! :)
